{"tid":1647372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大J一球懸紅點醒我地一樣嘢","createTime":"2019-10-11T17:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T17:28:36.000Z","uid":228995,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9db7a5dd7b6b72563294eb76362af2fb5dca9111","tid":1647372,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"Popo捉人唔止靠武力，仲靠情報。<br />\n同樣，香港人要防止警權坐大，靠嘅都唔能力靠武力，因為實力差太遠。<br />\n<br />\n謝振中移民係一個例子。<br />\n<br />\n你覺得佢放大假會係巧合嗎？如果popo高層知佢搞移民，高層仲會唔會將重要機密情報爆畀佢知？保安科又會唔會開file？怕謝sir做間諜？<br />\n<br />\n如果大J呢一球可以買到情報，唔一定係同今次運動有關。可以用懸紅買爆料。邊啲散仔借財仔？邊啲買外圍波？邊啲叫霸王雞？<br />\n<br />\n建立一套篤灰機制。重賞之下幫助警隊清走瘀血。革走不守紀律份子。<br />\n<br />\n你哋覺得自己好團結？香港人就要搞散你。"},{"pid":"c6093fc53b66597a24b0d523114d3c086110eab0","tid":1647372,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a1201c8d8f6e13c25a452fe94bae9d29e25bdf","tid":1647372,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:14:13.000Z","msg":"學藍c咁整網站籌旗買料"},{"pid":"615cc18f4211f55d4d5252c29ef740cde73c87e9","tid":1647372,"uid":161374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:17:23.000Z","msg":"大J做咁多野但仲未係最多人subscribe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但出錢又出力"},{"pid":"ea39a204539507cacd6f55e12fbaff1964bda338","tid":1647372,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f98d40af8e2a6d8005d05c6dd21969899a9931","tid":1647372,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:19:04.000Z","msg":"團咩結，咪都係為錢"},{"pid":"3bf0da360f84478ee1a96f316f60ecb692fb3cfe","tid":1647372,"uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:19:25.000Z","msg":"有數得計<br />\n<br />\n一條散仔由廿歲到退休人工完全有得計<br />\n<br 